data.name: itemsQuickInfo_lbl.Text
data.value: Welcome to the new items screen! Here you can still add items, but I have added quick picks for more popular items to add to a trainer. Don't worry, it won't mess with any itmes you have already added! Just click the button of the item, and it will add it for you!
